  "Description": {
    "English": "Upgrades the hyperdrive's computational matrix,  preventing temporal anomalies when attempting to reach rare-class <span class=\"name name-technology\">blue stellar bodies</span>.<br><br>User is advised to access Hyperdrive systems via the <VAL_ON>Galactic Map<>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "对超光速推进器的计算矩阵进行升级，避免在尝试抵达稀有级<span class=\"name name-technology\">蓝色星体</span>时遇到时空异常。<br><br>建议使用者通过<VAL_ON>银河星图<>接入超光速推进系统。",
    "TencentChinese": "超光速推进器保护矩阵已升级，现在能避免在尝试抵达稀有级<span class=\"name name-technology\">蓝色星球主体</span>时，出现现实故障。<br><br>建议用户通过<VAL_ON>星系图<>进入超光速推进系统。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "升級超空間驅動器防護矩陣，試圖接近罕見等級<span class=\"name name-technology\">藍色恆星體</span>時，能防止現實失常。<br><br>建議使用者透過<VAL_ON>銀河地圖<>存取超空間驅動器系統。"
  },
